Text:
Already had this one, But if you could keep an eye open for the dubbed version of Attack of the Mushroom People id appreciate it. The Gal lives in Texas and I live in Canada, so be fun to send both versions to her. 

   Ta!!

hhmm....tough nut to crack.  The subbed version is quite easy to track down for free, but the dubbed version for whatever reason is not quite so easy..  There are even sites that want $30.00 for the dubbed!!!  ROFL

I'll keep checkin..=)
